# Blog Project Overview

**Tech stack:** Astro 5, TypeScript (strict), Tailwind 4, MDX, React (Sandpack only), Pagefind

## Path Aliases

Use these instead of relative paths when importing:

- `@constants` → `src/constants.ts`
- `@utils` → `src/utils.ts`
- `@components/*` → `src/components/*`
- `@layouts/*` → `src/layouts/*`
- `@assets/*` → `src/assets/*`
- `@styles/*` → `src/styles/*`

```astro
// ✅ GOOD
import Seo from '@components/seo.astro'
import { SITE } from '@constants'
import { defaultDateFormat } from '@utils'

// ❌ BAD
import Seo from '../../components/seo.astro'
```

## Project Structure

- `src/components/` — Astro components; `a11y/` for accessibility components
- `src/layouts/` — Layout wrappers
- `src/pages/` — File-based routing; `[blog].astro` for dynamic routes
- `content/blog/` — Blog posts: `YYYY-MM-DD--slug/index.mdx`
- `src/constants.ts` — Site-wide config (SITE, HEADER, FRONTMATTER_TAGS, etc.)
- `src/utils.ts` — Shared utilities

## Formatting

- Prettier: tabs, singleQuote, semi, trailingComma es5, printWidth 100
- Imports: always at top of file (no inline imports)
